Expect PRs to be in states:
- Waiting for reviews (multiple PRs per author)
- Review failed, working on it (exactly one per author)
- Review failed, in my TODO (multiple PRs per author)
- Review succeeded, waiting for QA/in QA (multiple PRs per author)
! - QA failed, working on it (exactly one per author)
! - QA failed. in my TODO (multiple PRs per author)
- QA succeeded, to be rebased/waiting for TeamCity before merging
- Merged
